title: I Declare | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: I Declare | Joel Osteen
description:
If you want to reach your full potential, you have to tune out every negative thing that has been spoken over you. Instead, receive what God says about you. You are blessed, favored and anointed, and your best days are still out in front of you!

Together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
